HEADWORD: Albedo
<hw>Al*be"do</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L., fr.
<ets>albus</ets> white.]</ety> <def>Whiteness.</def>
<specif>Specifically:</specif> <fld>(Astron.)</fld> <def>The ratio which
the light reflected from an unpolished surface bears to the total light
falling upon that surface.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

